Open UP vision statement
    The problem of : 
            paperbased diet logs 
    affects:
            The quality of diet recommendation made by coaches to their members 
    the impact of which is:
            that coaches are not able to analyze diet-logs and the members do not get the expected value 
    A successful solution would be:
            a software application that makes it: 
                1. Easy for members to log their diets 
                2. Insightful for coaches to analyze their members diet logs 
With this information product vision can start.. refer to product vision